metadata.name: Stillness
metadata.description:
Once below the surface, the mind is the most important tool. 

Keeping yourself relaxed and focused on each movement is crucial, as our oxygen is limited. In order to achieve your goals, only the present matters; nothing else.

When you feel lost in the algorithm of life, remember to pause, breathe, and realize the importance of your choices.

At that moment, time stops.


By Livio Fakeye
